title: 249 - Flagship Track Pants
description:
MATERIAL: 100% Polyamide.

FIT: Loose.

DESIGN:  The flagship pants perfectly capture the essence of old-school style with their loose-fitting design and vintage aesthetics. These joggers, made of polyamide, offer durability. With no cuffs and two side strips in contrasting colors, they add a touch of uniqueness and style to your ensemble. Elevate your casual look to new heights.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'9.
